        {
            "title": "美國提供數千萬美元支持柬埔寨泰國停火協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國一位高級官員呼籲柬埔寨和泰國維護其爭議邊界沿線脆弱的停火協議，並承諾提供資金支持停火、排雷以及打擊跨國犯罪的努力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務院負責東亞和太平洋事務的助理國務卿邁克爾·德索姆布雷周五在聲明中稱，將提供1500萬美元用於邊境穩定，1000萬美元用於排雷和清除未爆彈藥，以及2000萬美元用於幫助兩國打擊詐騙活動和毒品走私的舉措。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泰國和柬埔寨在12月27日達成停火協議。之前在7月下旬也曾達成停火協議，但後來破裂。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e8c068e8-44a0-3d06-95d0-681569f350fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Offers Millions to Support Cambodia-Thailand Ceasefire</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-082141155.html",
