        {
            "title": "MiniMax在香港交易首日大漲91% 此前通過IPO募集6.19億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"572\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IYZkyBaTEQsZKPtf41bTgw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0f05ded8cefb85a7c2018df2a18ab3ac\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> MiniMax Group Inc.在香港交易首日飆升，這家中國生成式人工智能初創公司此前通過首次公開募股(IPO)籌集6.19億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MiniMax股價一度上漲91%，其發行價為每股165港元，公司行使了發售量調整權。公開發售部分獲得逾1,830倍認購。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司獲得阿里巴巴、阿布達比主權財富基金的支持，是中國「後ChatGPT時代」生成式人工智能企業中首批上市的公司之一。其競爭對手智譜周四上市交易首日表現平平。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-237d8884-6ee6-3705-a855-84913d382ee6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"572\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_YpmCCBMj4jVVNv8iEZCxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bd7c9e871877f40c238ffe17ed693c6c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大華繼顯香港執行董事Steven Leung表示，MiniMax的股價上漲既得到短期操作買家的支撐，也得到了長期機構投資者的支持。他指出，在人工智能泡沫的擔憂下，可能會有一些流動性從美國轉移過來。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MiniMax首日股價表現將成為檢驗中國AI板塊投資熱情能否從硬體公司延伸至軟件企業的試金石。受本土化需求推動，晶片製造商摩爾線程和沐曦股份在上市首日股價均實現數倍上漲，晶片設計商壁仞科技在香港交易首日則飆升76%。相比之下，智譜收盤僅上漲13%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與全球同行相比，中國AI投資周期仍處於早期階段，投資者可能難以分辨贏家和輸家，」彭博行業研究分析師Marvin Chen表示。「隨著周期成熟，表現可能開始出現更明顯的分化。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題MiniMax Jumps 91% in Hong Kong Debut After $619 Million IPO</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新股價表現及分析師評論)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/minimax%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B254-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8Eipo%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%866-19%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-020129899.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-09 15:40:53",
